name: EMIYA
title: Wrought Iron Hero
dialogue: Archer-class Servant. I have been summoned and come at your request.

name: Gilgamesh
title: Humanity's Oldest King
dialogue: Hahaha! For you to summon me like this, I see your luck has run out, Mongrel!

name: Robin Hood
title: Hunter of the Woods
dialogue: Okay, okay! I will get to work since I was summoned.

name: Atalanta
title: Hunter of Chastity
dialogue: Art thou my Master? Best Regards.

name: Euryale
dialogue: My name is Euryale. Rigght. I am a Goddess. It'll be one short life, but do your best to entertain me.

name: Arash
dialogue: I am Arash, Hero of the East. Nice to meet you!

name: Orion
dialogue: Artemis: Yeees! It's me, Arte-...I mean, Orion!Orion: This here is the somewhat-pet-somewhat-stuffed-animal Oribe. Nice to meet you!

name: David
dialogue: Archer David. Yes I will do it. Definitely will.

name: Oda Nobunaga
title: Demon King of the Sixth Heaven
dialogue: I am the Demon Archer Nobunaga, the Demon King of the Sixth Heaven!! Very well... I will allow you to be my Master!!

name: Nikola Tesla
title: Dr. Raiden
dialogue: I'm Nikola Tesla, the genius.

name: Arjuna
title: The Endowed Hero
dialogue: Servant, Archer. I'm Arjuna. Master, please command me as you wish.

name: Kid Gil
dialogue: Hello, Master. My name... Let me see... You can just call me Gil.

name: Billy the Kid
title: Juvenile Rascal King
dialogue: Hello! My name is Billy the Kid! Although I am a new Servant, I think I will be useful! Nice to meet you!

name: Tristan
dialogue: Knight of the Round Table, Tristan. I have arrived in answer to the summons. I pray that I will be useful to you. Please issue your order, Master.

name: Tawara Tōta
title: Fujiwara no Hidesato
dialogue: Yes, Servant Archer here to answer your summons. Our first order of business is a meal.

name: Artoria Pendragon (Archer)
dialogue: G-Good morning! Archer Altria, I have come to answer your summon. This is a class I am not used to, so I don't know if I can be of use. But please take care of  me!

name: Anne Bonny & Mary Read (Archer)
dialogue: Anne:  Here Master 1 This swimsuit... What do you think? Mary: ...where are you staring, Master? Hmph!

name: Chloe von Einzbern
dialogue: It seems you took care of me a lot. It'd be rude to say goodbye like this, so I'll return the favor. Yes, I'm sure you'll find me useful. After all, everyone knows the big sister is better at everything.

name: Ishtar
title: Goddess of Venus
dialogue: Yoohoo! You're looking as laid-back as ever!But I'm relieved. That's how you should be.Huh? You don't know me? You don't remember me?...I see. Well, that's no surprise, I guess.I am Ishtar, Goddess of Beauty and Governor of Venus.Fear me and do your best to satisfy me with tribute and reverence!

name: James Moriarty
title: Archer of Shinjuku
dialogue: Hahahaha! You must be a peculiar Master to have summoned me! My Class is Archer. For now, I shall hold off on revealing my True Name! But I am strong. That much I can guarantee!

name: EMIYA (Alter)
title: Emiya Shirou
dialogue: So you're my Master. You look hideous. Whatever. I may be in a strange getup, but I'm an Archer. Use me well.

name: Helena Blavatsky (Archer)
dialogue: I'm Helena Blavatsky, and I've changed my Saint Graph for a change of pace! I think it turned out pretty well for my first time! ...Though, I think there's probably another reason. Doing something like that shouldn't be this easy, right?

name: Tomoe Gozen
title: Archer Inferno
dialogue: I am Archer Inferno, and I came because of warfare. Yes, it is a temporary name, not my real name. Please forgive my rudeness.

name: Attila the San(ta)
dialogue: I’m Altera the San(ta). This sheep is my partner, Zerco. I’m still a novice Santa, but I can become a full-fledged one this way. I ask you to guide me to the Abyss, Master. ...Achoo.

name: Asagami Fujino
dialogue: Hello there, dear young mage. My name is Asagami Fujino. Let's see... my class is... Archer... I wonder if that's correct? What I'm capable of is to bend all things with my supernatural force, I hope it will be of some use...

name: Chiron
title: Great Sage of Centaurs
dialogue: Archer-class Servant, Chiron, has answered your summons. I hope my knowledge can can be of some help to you... In any case, nice to meet you. I'll use all of my strength for your sake.

name: Jeanne d'Arc (Archer)
dialogue: I've answered to your summons. I'm Jeanne! Since this time it's about Archer in vacation, so I'm avoiding stiff words here. So let's enjoy and have fun with our summer vacation.

name: Paris
dialogue: Y-yes! Archer, Paris. I’ve been summoned together with Lord Apollo! I may be unskilled, but I’ll do my best!

name: Osakabehime (Archer)
dialogue: E-Everyone, sorry to disturb you…… I’m Archer Osakabehime……. I did my best and put on a swimsuit…… H-How is it……? Does it suit me? It suits me, right? I chose it in desperation, so…… If you could say it suits me, I’d get some confidence…….

name: Artoria Pendragon
title: King of Knights of the Holy Sword
dialogue: Let me ask. Are you my Master?

name: Artoria Pendragon (Alter)
dialogue: ...I have come in response to your summon. Are you the one who is to be my Master?

name: Artoria Pendragon (Lily)
dialogue: It is nice to meet you Master. Since I am still in training, please call me Saber Lily. It is a pleasure to meet you.

name: Nero Claudius
title: Emperor of Roses
dialogue: Servant Saber. Nero Claudius, I have arrived in response to your call! Umu, you have chosen the right one! You sure know how to tell the difference!

name: Siegfried
title: Tenacious Dragon Slayer
dialogue: Saber, Siegfried. I have come in response to your summons. Please give me the order.

name: Gaius Julius Caesar
dialogue: Saber... Saber?I wonder what makes me a Saber?

name: Attila
title: Great King of Destruction
dialogue: My name is Altera....I am the Hun and I am a warrior serving the God of War.

name: Gilles de Rais (Saber)
dialogue: Saber, Gilles de Rais. I have come at your request.

name: Chevalier d'Eon
dialogue: My name is Chevalier d'Eon. I am the knight that will protect you and the royalty of France...Knight of the White Lily!

name: Okita Sōji
dialogue: I've arrived! Shinsengumi's First Unit Captain, Okita Souji!  Are you my Master? ...What? My haori? I...must have misplaced it...

name: Fergus mac Róich
dialogue: Hey, I'm a Saber-Class Servant. I have been summoned by your request.My name is Fergus mac Róich.Let's see... is Cú Chulainn here?

name: Mordred
title: Knight of Treachery
dialogue: I am Saber, name's Mordred. Is my father here?

name: Nero Claudius (Bride)
dialogue: Umu... I am back with a new dress! Call me Bride Saber, or Nero Bride!

name: Ryōgi Shiki (Saber)
dialogue: Saber-class Servant, Ryougi Shiki. I have answered your summons. ...Hehe, I wonder if this is good enough? I know there's a limit to being unique, but I am counting on you Master.

name: Lancelot (Saber)
dialogue: Saber-class Servant, Lancelot, has arrived.  It may be just for a moment, but I shall offer my sword to you, Master.

name: Gawain
title: Holy Sword of the Sun
dialogue: Knight of the Round Table, Gawain. I look forward to working with you.

name: Bedivere
title: The Silver Arm
dialogue: Saber, Bedivere. Henceforth, I shall become your Servant. I believe that is for the sake of my king.

name: Elizabeth Báthory (Brave)
dialogue: The party has gathered to venture forth! Are you ready? I, the new, graceful Saber Servant start my advance! With that said, give me some embers, please! Raise my level!

name: Miyamoto Musashi
title: Flower of Tengen
dialogue: Shinmen Musashi-no-Kami Fujiwara-no-Harunob...!? Sorry, let me start over! Servant Saber, Shinmen Musashi at your service! Make my stay a fun one, Master!

name: Arthur Pendragon (Prototype)
dialogue: I am Saber. I am a Servant who protects you and the world.

name: Suzuka Gozen
dialogue: Servant, Saber, I'm totally here 'cuz I was summoned! Or something like that★

name: Frankenstein (Saber)
dialogue: Saber-class Servant! Frankenstein's Monster. It's summer, and now I'm not so harsh! Let's get along, 'kay?

name: Yagyū Munenori
dialogue: Saber, Yagyū Tajima-no-Kami Munenori. From now on, I will be serving you as my Master. No matter what your command is, I shall obey.

name: Medb (Saber)
dialogue: At last it's here, here it is! In an long awaited swimsuit form, Queen Medb has manifested! Heroic spirits who can match up to my skin's value... there aren't any. Hey, don't you think so too?

name: Diarmuid Ua Duibhne (Saber)
dialogue: Servant, Saber. Diarmuid Ua Duibhne of the Knights of Fianna. Allow me to let you serve as a knight.

name: Beni-enma
title: Tongue-Cut Sparrow Benienma
dialogue: Welcome to the Enma Pavilion.  I am delighted to meet you, honorable guest...is not how it goes, right.  Servant; Saber. The Tongue-Cut Sparrow, Benienma. I have come here to offer my services.  Please take care of me from now on.

name: Jason
dialogue: Saber, Jason. I have arrived according to your summoning. I’m a hero but before that I’m a captain. Okay? Be careful not to send me to the front. Don’t ever send me out!

name: Cú Chulainn
title: Child of Light
dialogue: Lancer-class Servant! I have been summoned and come at your request. Let's take this easy Master!

name: Elizabeth Báthory
dialogue: Are you the new manager? Nice to meet you and please take care of me♡

name: Musashibō Benkei
title: Hitachibou Kaison
dialogue: I am Musashibō Benkei, and I have been reincarnated as a spearman! Best regards!

name: Cú Chulainn (Prototype)
dialogue: I am Cú Chulainn from Ulster, a Lancer-class servant. Nice to meet you!

name: Leonidas I
dialogue: Servant class, Lancer. Leonidas, King of Sparta. At your service!

name: Romulus
dialogue: ...Rome is Rome.

name: Hector
dialogue: Ho! I am Lancer, the name is Hektor. Have you heard of me? Oh no? Oh well, nice to meet you.

name: Scáthach
title: Queen of the Land of Shadows
dialogue: I came from the Land of Shadow. My name is Scáthach. I guess I should call you, Master?

name: Diarmuid Ua Duibhne
title: Beautiful Young Warrior
dialogue: I am the first spear of the Knights of Fianna, Diarmuid Ua Duibhne. I have arrived. I am now a Servant who serves you.

name: Artoria Pendragon (Lancer Alter)
dialogue: Lancer, Altria. I have been summoned upon your request. Just as my beloved horse can swallow the thunder clouds, my spear will break through every rampart. I will crush everything that stands in your way.

name: Fionn mac Cumhaill
dialogue: Erin's[1] Savior. The captain of the glorious Knights of Fianna.The man who rose to victory over Nuadha....Fionn mac Cumhaill is here.I'm counting on you, Master.

name: Li Shuwen (Lancer)
title: No Second Strike
dialogue: Servant, Lancer. My name is Li Shuwen. You can use me as a spear as you please.

name: Artoria Pendragon (Lancer)
title: Lion King
dialogue: I shall answer your call. I am your Servant, Lancer. With this lance, I will be your strength.

name: Tamamo no Mae (Lancer)
dialogue: Ta-daaa! I heard "beach" and came right away. Who called for this honeymoon? Servant Lancer, Tamamo-no-Mae. I am ready to take your heart away♡ Would you like to go on a summer adventure with me?

name: Kiyohime (Lancer)
dialogue: Ufufufufu. Master~ it's your Kiyohime! Though it's embarrassing to be exposing my skin to the public eye... but it's specially just for you, Master?

name: Vlad III (EXTRA)
dialogue: Servant Lancer. I am Vlad III. Dear friend. Every corruption, every injustice... Let us fight to end them all.

name: Jeanne d'Arc (Alter) (Santa Lily)
dialogue: I'm Jeanne! Although it's a bit early for Christmas, let's fight together! By the way, do you know how to work this sleigh?

name: Enkidu
dialogue: Servant, Lancer. Enkidu. Your call has activated me. Please use me as you wish. Mercy is unnecessary, Master.

name: Medusa (Lancer)
dialogue: I've materialized as a Lancer-class. My True Name is Medusa. I look forward to working with you.

name: Jaguar Man
title: Fujimura Taiga
dialogue: The mighty Jaguar Warrior is here! I'm not a tiger, so don't call me one! You over there, don't ignore me! I'm surprisingly strong if you try using me!

name: Minamoto no Raikō (Lancer)
dialogue: ...What's wrong, Master? Disturbs public morals? Now, what could you mean by that…...is there something wrong with how I look?

name: Parvati
title: Matou Sakura
dialogue: Hello, Master of Chaldea. I am known as the goddess Parvati. On this occasion, I’ve manifested by borrowing the body of a pure young girl. I’m inexperienced with this situation as well so, will you grow together with me?

name: Hōzōin Inshun
title: Lancer Purgatorio
dialogue: Were you surprised? Lancer, Hōzōin Inshun. Well then, I'll be in your care.

name: Nezha
dialogue: Servant, Lancer, Nata. ... That's it.

name: Ereshkigal
title: Tohsaka Rin
dialogue: Servant. Lancer. Mistress of the nether world, Ereshkigal.I came up to summon.It is against my will to lend power to one individual, but I'll give you a hand anyway as you've called me.Be grateful!...... ............ ...................I wonder why you are silent!What? I am a fine goddess!

name: Ibaraki Dōji (Lancer)
dialogue: Is there a festival around? I see I see. Hehehe. By tinkering with my Saint Graph, I became an oni that can have her fill at a festival, you know! I am Ibaraki Douji. One who would violate even festivals! ...munch munch

name: Bradamante
dialogue: One of Charlemagne's Twelve Paladins, the Knight of White Feathers, Bradamante. I have been summoned as a Lancer. On behalf of the Great King, I shall execute justice!

name: Nagao Kagetora
title: Uesugi Kenshin
dialogue: That’s right, Otora and all that is whatever, I’ll be using the name Lancer of the Eightfold Blossom (Hakka) for the time being.  I do have a bit of confidence when combat performance.  So for now, I shall be in your care!

name: Gareth
dialogue: I’m Gareth. ――― Seventh seat of the Round Table, I’m a knight that served King Arthur!

name: Mysterious Alter Ego Λ
dialogue: A shabbier summoning room than I thought……. Well, it’s fine. Rejoice, the most beautiful swan in this star has come. Ah, but don’t talk to me familiarly. I’m a top-star. I want to avoid scandals. Let’s see… Could you call me Mysterious Alter Ego Λ?

name: Medusa
title: Female Monster of Gorgon
dialogue: ...You have strange preferences. If you require a sacrifice, do feel free to command me as you wish.

name: Georgios
dialogue: Rider Georgios. I did hear your summons and answered the call. Let us do our best.

name: Edward Teach
dialogue: My goodness! what a coincidence! Fahaha! Blackbeard has come to see you! Green is the enemy!

name: Boudica
dialogue: My name is Boudica, nice to meet you! Don't mind the formalities.

name: Ushiwakamaru
title: Minamoto no Yoshitsune
dialogue: I am Ushiwakamaru and I have been called upon. Honoring the full devotion as a Samurai, I will do mu utmost best!

name: Alexander
dialogue: My name is Alexander. And You can call also call me Alexander the Third. Of course other nicknames are welcome too.

name: Marie Antoinette
dialogue: Do you like me too? Very well, then let's... If so, that's great... Vive La France!

name: Martha
dialogue: My name is Martha, just plain Martha...We will save the world without fail!

name: Francis Drake
title: Voyager of the Storm
dialogue: Are you the new Master? I'm Francis Drake. Well, I hope we can work well together.

name: Anne Bonny & Mary Read
dialogue: Mary: Were you surprised? The two of us are one Servant. Anne: She is Mary Read. I'm Anne Bonny. Pleased to meet you.

name: Artoria Pendragon (Santa Alter)
dialogue: Merry Christmas, excuse me for entering from the chimney. I am the pretty Santa Claus who has answered your summon. You must be my reindeer?

name: Astolfo
title: Knight of Evaporated Sanity
dialogue: Yahoo! My name is Astolfo! Rider Class! And, and...umm, nice to meet you!

name: Medb
title: Queen of Connacht
dialogue: I am Medb. Queen Medb! Are you the might warrior, the one who will fight and die for me?

name: Iskandar
title: The King of Conquerors of the Distant Lands
dialogue: Oh you have done well to summon me! Iskandar, King of Conquerors, shall carve out your path!

name: Sakata Kintoki (Rider)
dialogue: Let's do this, Master! What? I'm a bit funkier than usual? No kidding! I'm a biker now, man! A rider!

name: Ozymandias
title: King of GodsPharaoh
dialogue: My name is Ozymandias, King of Kings. Look on my works, ye Mighty, and despair!

name: Mordred (Rider)
dialogue: Yah-hoo, Master! I came to play! Ah, keep it a secret from father! I snuck this board out secretly!

name: Quetzalcoatl
dialogue: Hiiii! The Goddess Quetzalcoatl arrives in the ring! Huh? I expected nude priests, but you're an adorable little summoner. Heehee, I don't suppose you're interested in tall, older women?

name: Christopher Columbus
title: Rider of Resistance
dialogue: I'm the Rider of Resistance... Well, nice to meet you.

name: Artoria Pendragon (Rider Alter)
dialogue: Rider-class Servant, Altria Pendragon. Now that I'm here, brace yourself to begin living your life properly! There will be no more going back to sleep once your alarm goes off, and no more letting yourself get out of shape. I will clean everything! I will do the laundry! C-cooking... Well, I'll do my best...

name: Ishtar (Rider)
title: Tohsaka Rin
dialogue: Rider Ishtar here. As a super special perk, I'll help you out this time. Let's just call it a little quid pro quo arrangement.

name: Achilles
title: The Swift Hero
dialogue: You drew a great Servant! Anyway, I'm the Rider-class Servant, Achilles. ...Yeah, yeah, the Heroic Spirit well-known for having his heel as his weak point. Well, to catch a hold of my heel is not something just anyone could do, you know! The name, "mankind's fastest legs", is not just for show, you know?

name: Sakamoto Ryōma
title: Hero of Restoration
dialogue: Ryōma: 「I am Rider, Sakamoto Ryōma. I run a detective office in this capital. I'll be counting on you for a while. Ah, I'll be happy if you also help with my detective work.」 Oryō-san:「And Oryō-san is a helper dragon. It is hard work, but if you put in effort, I'll give you a frog.」

name: Sima Yi (Reines)
title: Reines El-Melloi Archisorte
dialogue: He, so you’ve summoned me. Sima Zhongda is here… Er, hm, I’m a Pseudo-Servant with Reines El-Melloi Archisorte, though? It’s fine it’s fine, the power is handed over. You can call me Reines, Sima Yi, or Zhongda, whichever you want. Take care of me, Master

name: Leonardo Da Vinci (Rider)
dialogue: Servant, Rider. There was this and that, so I became the second Da Vinci-chan. I may not be as reliable as the previous me, but make a beautiful use of me, Master-kun

name: Bartholomew Roberts
dialogue: Fufu, you’re quite lucky. Bartholomew Roberts. I’ve arrived in response to the summoning request. Well then, let us orderly be diligent in the pirate business

name: Carmilla (Rider)
dialogue: My, what an unexpected meeting. …The atmosphere is different from usual? Fufu, is that so? At any rate, I think that me being a dangerous woman hasn’t changed. Be as careful as possible, Master

name: Medea
title: Witch of Perfidies
dialogue: Oh my, you are a rather cute Master!

name: Gilles de Rais
title: Holy Monster
dialogue: I am Gilles de Rais, and I have come to you at your invitation. From here on, I shall be at your command.

name: Hans Christian Andersen
dialogue: I am a third-rate servant, Andersen. Just throw me in the corner of a bookshelf.

name: William Shakespeare
title: The Greatest Writer
dialogue: I am Caster-class Shakespeare, and I have come to see you! So, shall we begin our story?

name: Mephistopheles
dialogue: Looks like you hit the jackpot, Master? I am the devil, Mephistopheles. And I have been called upon.

name: Wolfgang Amadeus Mozart
dialogue: I am Amadeus Wolfgang Mozart! Leave battles aside, I promise only to decorate your life!

name: Zhuge Liang (Lord El-Melloi II)
title: Waver Velvet
dialogue: I am Servant Zhuge Liang...What? You are asking if I am the wrong person? Exactly, I am actually El-Melloi the Second. But I did inherit all the powers, so there's no issue there.

name: Cú Chulainn (Caster)
title: Child of Light
dialogue: Oops! I guess this time I am materialized as a Caster? Oh, it's you guys! We met before right?

name: Elizabeth Báthory (Halloween)
dialogue: Trick or treat! There's no need for introductions, right? Demoness Elisabeth Báthory. In response to your passionate support, I have been summoned in my best dress!

name: Tamamo no Mae
title: Fox Priestess of Peerless Beauty
dialogue: I will always be there for you! Your reliable Shrine Maiden Fox, Caster, has now arrived!

name: Medea (Lily)
dialogue: I'm Medea, a Caster-class Servant. I look forward to working with you.

name: Nursery Rhyme
dialogue: Hello to the wonderful you. Let's make this a beautiful dream.

name: Paracelsus von Hohenheim
dialogue: I have been summoned upon your request. Please, be friends with me, Paracelsus.

name: Charles Babbage
title: Dream of Steam
dialogue: My name is Steam King. I died once and now my existance lives along in the imaginary world.

name: Helena Blavatsky
dialogue: ...It's all right. This Caster will guide you along the way!

name: Thomas Edison
title: The Wizard of Menlo Park
dialogue: Servant, Caster. I am Thomas Alva Edison! Don't worry about my looks! This is the symbol of America!

name: Geronimo
dialogue: Servant class, Caster. …Maybe I'm known better as Geronimo.

name: Irisviel (Dress of Heaven)
dialogue: I am from the Holy Grail. The one serving as the terminal of the Holy Grail. A temporary form. A temporary Servant. My name... Please call me Irisviel.

name: Xuanzang Sanzang
title: The Bonze of Tang Dynasty
dialogue: My name is Xuanzang Sanzang! Through the guidance of the Buddha, I have arrived! Umm, I am a Caster!

name: Nitocris
title: Avatar of the Sky
dialogue: "Servant, Caster. Reincarnation of the Sky God Horus, I, Nitocris have answered your summons. As you can see, I am a pharaoh, but vastly inexperienced. Thus, for now I shall accept you as my ally. However, I have one thing to say. Bow your head. You're being disrespectful!"

name: Leonardo Da Vinci
dialogue: Nice to meet you once again. I am servant Leonardo Da Vinci. Yes, from now on, I will be Da Vinci-chan only for you!

name: Marie Antoinette (Caster)
dialogue: I like beaches, I really do! I hope you and everyone can enjoy it, too! -Vive La France! Oh? There's a crab sitting on my head. Hehehe, How are you, Mr. Crab?

name: Illyasviel von Einzbern
dialogue: Illya - Erm, I'm called Illya. I'm a 5th elementary school grader. For now... I'm trying out being a magical girl, yes. Uhm, I'm not sure if someone like me will be useful……But I'll do my very best! Ruby - Ruby-chan is here too! Let's go with plenty of cuteness and , Grand Master!

name: Gilgamesh (Caster)
title: Sovereign of Magic Wands
dialogue: Caster, Gilgamesh. I have materialized in this form to meet Uruk's time of need, not in response to your summon. Don't get cocky, mongrel.

name: Merlin
dialogue: Greetings, Master of Chaldea. I am merlin. People call me the Mage of Flowers. Just call me Merlin. I don't care for formalities.

name: Scheherazade
title: Caster of Nightless City
dialogue: Do you called for me? I am now a Caster of the nocturnal castle... Someday, I will tell you my real name, probably, the time I have to do it when I don't want to die.

name: Nero Claudius (Caster)
dialogue: Surprised by the sudden swimsuit? I bet you're surprised! Umu, I am ecstatic too! My heart is racing! Caster, Nero Claudius, here to answer your summon! Let's make this an unforgettable summer!

name: Circe
title: Caster of Okeanos
dialogue: I’m Caster of Okeanos. I won’t let you be lonely anymore. Since you’ve called upon this Witch of Hawks. Fufu.

name: Queen of Sheba
title: Caster of Midrash
dialogue: Yes, I'm here~. For now, the Caster of Midrash? Please, call me that. I'll be useful, you know?

name: Sieg
dialogue: For the moment being, this is a temporary contract. This is not my first experience fighting as a servant, but this is the first time I fight as myself... I think I’m saying a lot of incomprehensible things, but I’m counting on you.

name: Shuten Dōji (Caster)
title: Gohou Shoujo Oni-Cure
dialogue: Eeer, well. The oni's…… How was it? In short, Dharmapala. That's right, the me now is a Dharmapala Girl. Since I'm an oni that controls onis, I can't ally with humans…… Fufu. Pardon me, 'kay?

name: Miyu Edelfelt
title: Sakatsuki Miyu
dialogue: Miyu: I'm Miyu. My surname is, temporarily, Edelfelt.  Sapphire: I'm named the Stick Magical Sapphire. ……I hope my older sister hasn't troubled you?

name: Murasaki Shikibu
title: Fujiwara no Kaoruko
dialogue: Servant, Caster. I'm called Murasaki Shikibu.  I'm a woman who befriends sentences, who gathers words,  who nestles close to the feelings of people, so……  Please use me at your own discretion……

name: Chen Gong
dialogue: Servant, Caster. My full name is Chen Gong, and my courtesy name is Gongtai. Being summoned like this is part of destiny. Let us associate for many years to come.

name: Sasaki Kojirō
title: Nameless Master
dialogue: I am Sasaki Kojirou, an Assassin-class Servant. And I have been called upon to your service.

name: Hassan of the Cursed Arm
title: Assassin of The White Skull
dialogue: Assassin-class Servant. I heard your call from the shadows.

name: Stheno
dialogue: Haha. Trying to summon a goddess to this world, such an interesting and poor soul. You, what is your name?

name: Jing Ke
dialogue: My name is Jing Ke, an Assassin-class Servant. I do feel complicated for being summoned after that failure. But let's plan well next time!

name: Charles-Henri Sanson
dialogue: My name is Charles-Henri Sanson. I have been summoned and come at your request!

name: Phantom of the Opera
dialogue: Whoever sees my face will learn the meaning of fear...including you.

name: Mata Hari
dialogue: Assassin-class Servant. I go by the name of Mata Hari. Nice to meet you.

name: Carmilla
dialogue: Ah. I guess this must be fate. Please call me Carmilla. I am an Assassin-class Servant.

name: Jack the Ripper
title: Innocent Murderer
dialogue: Assassin Jack the Ripper. Nice to meet you, Mother.

name: Henry Jekyll & Hyde
title: Double Entities
dialogue: My name is Jekyll. I am...different from Hyde.

name: Mysterious Heroine X
dialogue: Code Name: Heroine X. I am a Servant summoned to deal with the recent problem of the ever-increasing number of Sabers appearing. Nice to meet you.

name: Ryōgi Shiki (Assassin)
dialogue: Is it your first time in a haunted house? It's pretty common in any populated city...  Well, follow me as far as you can without dying.

name: EMIYA (Assassin)
title: Emiya Kiritsugu
dialogue: More dirty work huh...Doesn't matter, happens all the time.

name: Hassan of the Hundred Faces
title: Leader of Hashasheen
dialogue: Now that you have command over the army of shadows, victory is at hand. You can rest easy now, Master.

name: Shuten Dōji
dialogue: Assassin, Shuten-Douji. Fufu. Please accept my gratitude for summoning me. I will do as I please but... you don't mind, do you?

name: Fūma Kotarō
dialogue: Servant, Assassin. Fuuma Kotarou. I might look like this, but please don't let that bother you...

name: Hassan of the Serenity
dialogue: Everything, everything, everything as you would will it. I will offer all of myself to you. This body, this heart, all of it...

name: Scáthach (Assassin)
dialogue: Servant, Assassin. I am Scáthach. I adjusted my Spirit Origin a little to match the environment. Well, I suppose you don't mind. I look forward to working with you.

name: Cleopatra
dialogue: "Hah, did you think I would appear from within a rolled-up carpet? ...Well, perhaps I considered it, but rejected the idea since this is our first meeting. I am the last Pharaoh, Cleopatra VII Philopator. Master, could you please refrain from holding your head higher than the sun?"

name: "The Old Man of the Mountain"
dialogue: Fear not, contractor. The Old Man of the Mountain hath come in answer to thy summons. I have no name. Address me as thou wilt.

name: Yan Qing
title: Assassin of Shinjuku
dialogue: "Well, well, I'm the Assassin you've summoned up! My True Name is a secret! Whaa~t, I'm sure you'll find out soon enough!"

name: Wu Zetian
title: Assassin of Nightless City
dialogue: I am the master if the righteous shining metropolis, Assassin of the Nightless City! That will do for now. If I revealed my True Name, you'd be too busy prostrating yourself to me to do anything else!

name: Nitocris (Assassin)
dialogue: I...am...a...nameless...pharaoh... Bow...your...head. Disrespect...disrespectful......Hey. Do...not...look...inside!

name: Mochizuki Chiyome
title: Assassin Paraíso
dialogue: Assassin Paraiso, Hasten to join in. I offer my loyalty to my new owner. Please forgive me to not reveal my true name. I'm prepared to take any punishment

name: Katō Danzō
dialogue: Katou Danzou. Activated. Requesting input, Master. As Danzou is a shinobi, I will obey any command.

name: Osakabehime
dialogue: Oh? Ah, yes, yes, I'm Osakabehime the Assasin. Hey, can I go home yet? Oh really.

name: Semiramis
title: Empress of Assyria
dialogue: Servant, Assassin. Semiramis. Now then... First, prepare a throne. We will talk only after that. If you have none then that cannot be helped, instead you should serve as the chair.

name: Okada Izō
title: Manslayer Izō
dialogue: I'm Tosa's Okada Izō. You might know me better as Hitokiri Izō. What? Assassin...? You misunderstood, my class is 'Hitokiri.'[1]

name: Ushiwakamaru (Assassin)
title: Minamoto no Yoshitsune
dialogue: It seems that after changing into a swimsuit I strangely became closer to the epoch when I was training. At the Kurama mount, playing is training, that's what I was taught. Therefore, that's the right path now. My lord, play a lot with Ushiwaka, please!

name: Kama
dialogue: Sigh……  Truth be told, I didn't plan to get in the way so much, but there are various circumstances.  I'm Kama, the god of love.  But I think it's better if you didn't consult me about love, you know?

name: Charlotte Corday
title: Angel of Assassination
dialogue: I’ve come in response to your summon! Assassin, Charlotte Corday! I’ll do my best, but sorry if I fail!

name: Heracles
title: The Immortal Great Hero
dialogue: I’ve come in response to your summon! Assassin, Charlotte Corday! I’ll do my best, but sorry if I fail!

name: Lancelot
title: Knight of the Lake
dialogue: Shuhuhuhuhuhuhuhuhu...

name: Lu Bu Fengxian
dialogue: Shuhuhuhuhuhuhuhuhu...

name: Spartacus
title: Gladiator of Thrace
dialogue: I am Berserker Spartacus.Sorry to ask this, but are you a tyrant?

name: Sakata Kintoki
dialogue: Ohh, Nice to meet you! I am sorry to trouble you for now. Just call me Golden.

name: Vlad III
title: Lord Impaler
dialogue: I am here at your request... Are you the Master who shall offer me your blood?

name: Asterios
dialogue: Whoooo!!

name: Caligula
dialogue: My... Action... Is... My... Destiny...

name: Kiyohime
dialogue: I am Servant Kiyohime. Do I look like a Berserker to you? It is nice to meet you, my Master.

name: Eric Bloodaxe
dialogue: Uraaaaaaaaaaaaa!

name: Tamamo Cat
dialogue: I am one of the Tamamo Nine, the Wild Fox, Tamamo Cat! Nice to meet you, my Master!

name: Frankenstein
title: Innocent Bride
dialogue: ...Uhhhhhhhhhh.

name: Beowulf
dialogue: Servant, Berserker. True Name's Beowulf. Well then, let's beat some things up, Master. ……Hey, hey, don't back off.

name: Nightingale
title: Angel of Crimea
dialogue: Please rest assured now that I'm here. Let's save everyone's lives. Even if all loves will be sacrificed.

name: Cú Chulainn (Alter)
dialogue: "I am Cú Chulainn, summoned at your request! ...My color has nothing to do with you."

name: Minamoto no Raikō
dialogue: Hello, my dear Mage. Servant, Saber... Oh? Huh? I am not a Saber... Oh dear. Erm... I am Minamoto-no-Raikou. Although I still have a long way to go, I will be counting on you from now on, okay?

name: Ibaraki Dōji
dialogue: My name is Ibaraki-Douji, the leader of the oni clan on Mt. Ooe.

name: Mysterious Heroine X (Alter)
dialogue: Heroine X Alter... I am a Berser... I mean, Saber-class... Yes, Saber, probably... Don't you think this room is rather cold? Can I just hack up that useless heater there?

name: Hijikata Toshizō
dialogue: Shinsengumi Vice Commander, Hijikata Toshizo.  My Class? That's irrelevant.  As long as I'm here, this...is...the Shinsengumi.

name: Chacha
dialogue: I am Chacha, the Sun's favorite concubine! I'm a Berserker Servant! Yep, I've given up on my class!

name: Penthesilea
title: Berserker of El Dorado
dialogue: Berserker of El Dorado... That is what they call me. That should suffice for now.

name: Paul Bunyan
dialogue: Enchanté... My name is Paul Bunyan. I'm a Berserker Nice to meet  you, Master. I wonder why I'm a girl... Strange, isn't it?

name: Oda Nobunaga (Berserker)
dialogue: Yeeeeeeaaah! Are you all pumped in!? I am the Demon King of the Sixth Heaven of the Beach.. That's right! Nobunaga THE Rock n' Roller! Eh? What part is rockin' you ask? A summer swimsuit means ROCK! Obviously! It's all about feeling, you know? Don't think too hard... Just feel! My Class is Berserker. Rockin' to meetcha!

name: Jeanne d'Arc (Berserker Alter)
dialogue: It is only temporary for now. Since I've changed into swimsuit, let's enjoy Hawaii to the fullest, Master... My saint graph was altered and I am now a berserker but, well it's a trivial detail.

name: Mori Nagayoshi
title: Demon Musashi
dialogue: I’m the Oni Musashi, Mori Nagayoshi!  My class was Berserker, right.  If you say something stupid I’ll cut you up immediately! … Hey hey, relax. I won't do something as cruel as killin' my Master. Well, I’m countin’ on ya, Master!

name: Salome
dialogue: I’m Salome! Herod’s daughter, Salome. You’re Master-san, right? Nice to meet you. …………Hey, you, do you like kissing?

name: Miyamoto Musashi (Berserker)
title: Flower of Tengen
dialogue: I did it! Berserker, Musashi Miyamoto, has been summoned here! But really, is it finally my swimsuit debut……? Fufu, I was interested on it since long ago so I’m really lucky! 	I’ll count on you for this one summer adventure, Master!

name: Jeanne d'Arc
title: Holy Maiden of Salvation
dialogue: Servant Ruler, Jeanne d'Arc. I'm really glad to meet you!

name: Amakusa Shirō
title: The One who Sought for an Endless Dream
dialogue: Ruler-class Servant. Amakusa Shirou Tokisada. Do I look like someone you know? I am sure it's only a coincidence.

name: Martha (Ruler)
dialogue: Martha has arrived once more. No matter my appearance, I am still me! Without fail, I shall save the world with you.

name: Sherlock Holmes
title: The One who Illuminates the Truth
dialogue: Are introductions necessary? I am a detective.If you were expecting a hero, my apologies...But if you wanted a detective or an investigator, you drew the right card.

name: Quetzalcoatl (Samba/Santa)
dialogue: I misunderstood it a bit, but giving out presents while dancing samba sounds fun? Santa and Samba, this is something doubly good! Leave it to me, Master! In order to retrieve the right Christmas, I'll do my best!

name: Astraea
title: Luviagelita Edelfelt
dialogue: I have come in response to your summons. The judgment of heaven, the justice of the stars is present. To all that is good in this world, I am called Astraea. As a master, are you prepared to be measured?

name: Edmond Dantès
title: The Count of Monte Cristo
dialogue: You called me! The reincarnation of vengence itself? Well precisely, I am the grudge of darkness I am Extra Class, Avenger!

name: Jeanne d'Arc (Alter)
title: Dragon Witch
dialogue: Servant, Avenger. Summoned upon your request. ...What's with that look? Come on, here's the contract.

name: Angra Mainyu
dialogue: Hey there! The weakest Heroic Spirit Avenger, I responded immediately when I heard your call!

name: Gorgon
dialogue: ...Hmph. Avenger, Gorgon. Use me well. I shall use you well, too. Whose untimely end will be displayed first? It should be something to see.

name: Demon King Nobunaga
dialogue: To make me an Avenger… Uhahaha! What a karmic thing. Very well! Make sure to engrave the Demon King of Sixth Heaven, Nobunaga’s lifestyle in your soul!

name: Meltlilith
dialogue: I'm the Alter Ego of pleasure, Meltryllis. I'd really rather not, but I suppose I'll form a contract with you. You should be honored, okay?

name: Passionlip
dialogue: ...I'm Passionlip...the Alter Ego of love and hate... Um... I'm sorry if I hurt you...

name: Sesshōin Kiara
dialogue: Alter Ego, Sessyoin Kiara. I have come to answer the voices calling for salvation. But...hehe... I wonder about the sort of person who would summon a woman like me. I am the Devilish Bodhisattva who savors all living creatures, sentient or not. You have now choice now but to stay with me until the very end.

name: Mecha Eli-chan
dialogue: I am Magus Aegis Elizabeth Channel. That is long, so Mecha Eli-chan is acceptable....Elizabeth is constantly presenting issues for you, but this time, I am the one imposing. Particularly, I have accepted you as my pilot. Please, do not misuse me.

name: Okita Sōji (Alter)
title: Majin Saber
dialogue: My name is Majin Okita Souji. I have manifested in response to your summons. Until this body's Saint Graph is smashed apart..., let's fight together.

name: Kingprotea
dialogue: Master...Master...Alter Ego, Kingprotea...has answered your summons... Am I big? Or small...?

name: Abigail Williams
dialogue: Hello! I’m Abigail--- Abigail Williams. I’m from the, Fo...reigner...class. Are you the Master? If it’s okay with you, please call me Abby. I believe we’ll quickly become friends.

name: Katsushika Hokusai
title: Katsushika Oui
dialogue: Katsushika Hokusai. A humble painter. Are you the Master? Oh, a fairly picturesque personage. Well, I'll paint even without permission.

name: Mysterious Heroine XX
dialogue: Katsushika Hokusai. A humble painter. Are you the Master? Oh, a fairly picturesque personage. Well, I'll paint even without permission.

name: B B
title: Mysterious Black Magus
dialogue: No world or barrier can hold me! I have finally come to the famous Chaldea! The lovely butterfly of the moon...BB, the Moon Cancer, has been summoned! Well, this is just a temporary arrangement, but take good care of me, Seeenpaaai<3

name: B B (Summer)
dialogue: To think that I would be summoned, so a human who doesn't know their place exists too, huh. By any chance, are you a little pain in the neck who wishes for the life of a piggy? Just kidding, the reward-like talk ends here. The Moon Cancer-class BB has come to grant your wish☆. Please, resign yourself to becoming my toy, okay, Se・n・pa・i?

name: Mashu Kyrielight
dialogue: I'm still just an immature Servant, but I'll do what I can to help you.
